description.en:
$FIRST is a community of creatives and innovators founded by music artist Harrison First.

$FIRST is powered by unique AUDIO NFTs and an awesome network of creators. One of the leading attributes from the community is $FIRST AUDIO which is a way for digital artists and nft creators to have access to a vault of music produced by Harrison First to use in your own NFTs.

All instrumentals are produced by Harrison First, and you are only required to hold 1,000 $FIRST to have access to the vault.

All those who hold 1K $FIRST also have access to the entire club and network on Discord.
